{"aid": "igkpb5eifk83fz", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 5, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6xxjjocYdf", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-29T13:26:50Z", "content": "<p>系统会将 memmap 的所有 E820_ARM 类型的内存块都调用一次 init_memmap&#xff0c;尽管实际上只发生了一次调用&#xff0c;但有没有可能有多个内存块的情况&#xff1f;buddy system 只能用在一个连续的内存块上&#xff0c;这样的话是不是还需要在应用 buddy system 之前使用其它内存分配算法&#xff08;如 first fit&#xff09;来选择一块内存&#xff1f;</p>", "subject": "实现 buddy system 的疑问"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446635305242, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-03-29T13:43:26Z", "id": "i7uhz3ze64p52p", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-29T13:43:26Z", "content": "<p>init_memmap是对每一块E820_ARM调用一次&#xff0c;请阅读kern/mm/pmm.c里的page_init函数。</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "i6xxjjocYdf", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-30T15:54:33Z", "id": "i7w23kpt5a530o", "updated": "2015-03-30T15:54:33Z", "subject": "<p>我知道会对每一块 E820_ARM 都调用一次 init_memmap&#xff0c;但 buddy system 只能用于一块连续的内存&#xff0c;因此在应用 buddy system 之前要先使用其它内存分配算法&#xff08;如 first fit&#xff09;来选择一块内存&#xff0c;或是只对一块内存应用 buddy system&#xff0c;不知道这样理解对不对。</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 4, "bucket_name": "This week", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [{"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "created": "2015-03-31T03:02:20Z", "id": "i7wpycio2j02ir", "updated": "2015-03-31T03:02:20Z", "subject": "<p>Buddy System可以同时应用到多块内存上&#xff0c;只需要每一块内存单独划分block即可&#xff0c;free_list仍然使用同一个。</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 4, "bucket_name": "This week", "children": [], "type": "feedb